><div class="Button_contentWrapper__ek4Um">수강생 후기</div></button></a><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="/blog/category/%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%A4%ED%8A%B8"><button class="Button_button___Dadr Button_text__PASZq gray GlobalHeader_menuButton__A0BI3 large" type="button"><div class="Button_contentWrapper__ek4Um">이벤트</div></button></a><div class="GlobalHeader_separator__DPXcC"></div><a href="/signin"><button class="Button_button___Dadr Button_text__PASZq gray GlobalHeader_menuButton__A0BI3 large" type="button"><div class="Button_contentWrapper__ek4Um">로그인</div></button></a></div><div class="GlobalHeader_mobileButtonWrapper__ECPVb GlobalHeader_right__keAA9"><a href="/signin"><button class="Button_button___Dadr Button_text__PASZq gray GlobalHeader_menuButton__A0BI3 large" type="button"><div class="Button_contentWrapper__ek4Um">로그인</div></button></a></div></nav></div><main class="GlobalLayout_main__HrdSm white"><div class="LayoutV2_container__hSyGM"><div id="landing-hero" data-section-name="hero" class="Hero_container__aTNIm"><div class="Hero_content__ajQRg"><div class="Hero_reviews__yCvzR"><div class="Hero_reviewContainer__FMklZ"><div class="Card_container__pb9Ya"><div class="Label_label__UEEIG Label_green__yc97x"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="thumbUp"><path d="M11.5 7.74983V4.74983C11.5 3.50718 10.4927 2.49982 9.25 2.49982L6.25 9.24983V17.4998H14.965C15.713 17.5083 16.3529 16.9644 16.465 16.2248L17.5 9.47483C17.566 9.0397 17.4377 8.59754 17.1489 8.26545C16.8601 7.93337 16.4401 7.74483 16 7.74983H11.5Z" fill="white" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M6.25 9.16693H4.2475C3.36888 9.15139 2.61779 9.87918 2.5 10.75V16C2.61779 16.8708 3.36888 17.5155 4.2475 17.5H6.25V9.16693Z" fill="var(--label-text-color)" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>프로젝트 만족</div><div class="Card_contentWrapper__opy6W"><div class="Card_content__NS5ju"><img alt="&quot;&quot;" loading="lazy" width="40" height="28" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Card_quote__kt5XP" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 1x, https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 2x" src="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover"/><div class="Card_contentText__rQUT9"><b>프로젝트를 하며 단계별로 성장하는 게 느껴졌습니다.</b> 모호하던 개념이 확실히 이해되고, 부족한 부분을 알 수 있는 계기가 되었습니다.</div></div><div class="Card_caption__BunOL">스프린트 수료생 | 윤OO 님</div></div></div></div><div class="Hero_reviewContainer__FMklZ"><div class="Card_container__pb9Ya"><div class="Label_label__UEEIG Label_red__U2v_K"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="thumbUp"><path d="M11.5 7.74983V4.74983C11.5 3.50718 10.4927 2.49982 9.25 2.49982L6.25 9.24983V17.4998H14.965C15.713 17.5083 16.3529 16.9644 16.465 16.2248L17.5 9.47483C17.566 9.0397 17.4377 8.59754 17.1489 8.26545C16.8601 7.93337 16.4401 7.74483 16 7.74983H11.5Z" fill="white" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M6.25 9.16693H4.2475C3.36888 9.15139 2.61779 9.87918 2.5 10.75V16C2.61779 16.8708 3.36888 17.5155 4.2475 17.5H6.25V9.16693Z" fill="var(--label-text-color)" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>훈련환경 및 장비 만족</div><div class="Card_contentWrapper__opy6W"><div class="Card_content__NS5ju"><img alt="&quot;&quot;" loading="lazy" width="40" height="28" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Card_quote__kt5XP" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 1x, https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 2x" src="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover"/><div class="Card_contentText__rQUT9"><b>오프라인 공간 환경이 정말 좋아요.</b> 팀미팅 공간이 있어 카페에 가지 않아도 된다는 점도 좋습니다.</div></div><div class="Card_caption__BunOL">스프린트 수료생 | 오OO 님</div></div></div></div><div class="Hero_reviewContainer__FMklZ"><div class="Card_container__pb9Ya"><div class="Label_label__UEEIG Label_green__yc97x"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="thumbUp"><path d="M11.5 7.74983V4.74983C11.5 3.50718 10.4927 2.49982 9.25 2.49982L6.25 9.24983V17.4998H14.965C15.713 17.5083 16.3529 16.9644 16.465 16.2248L17.5 9.47483C17.566 9.0397 17.4377 8.59754 17.1489 8.26545C16.8601 7.93337 16.4401 7.74483 16 7.74983H11.5Z" fill="white" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M6.25 9.16693H4.2475C3.36888 9.15139 2.61779 9.87918 2.5 10.75V16C2.61779 16.8708 3.36888 17.5155 4.2475 17.5H6.25V9.16693Z" fill="var(--label-text-color)" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>프로젝트 만족</div><div class="Card_contentWrapper__opy6W"><div class="Card_content__NS5ju"><img alt="&quot;&quot;" loading="lazy" width="40" height="28" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Card_quote__kt5XP" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 1x, https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 2x" src="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover"/><div class="Card_contentText__rQUT9">프로젝트를 통해 <b>문제 해결 능력, 효율적인 커뮤니케이션</b> 방법 등을 배울 수 있었습니다.</div></div><div class="Card_caption__BunO