ju"><img alt="&quot;&quot;" loading="lazy" width="40" height="28" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Card_quote__kt5XP" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 1x, https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 2x" src="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover"/><div class="Card_contentText__rQUT9"><b>적응이 늦는 스프린터분들을 따로 도와주시는</b> 부분에서 관리가 잘 되고 있다고 느꼈습니다.</div></div><div class="Card_caption__BunOL">스프린트 수료생 | 권OO 님</div></div></div></div><div class="Hero_reviewContainer__FMklZ"><div class="Card_container__pb9Ya"><div class="Label_label__UEEIG Label_yellow__EMyGK"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="thumbUp"><path d="M11.5 7.74983V4.74983C11.5 3.50718 10.4927 2.49982 9.25 2.49982L6.25 9.24983V17.4998H14.965C15.713 17.5083 16.3529 16.9644 16.465 16.2248L17.5 9.47483C17.566 9.0397 17.4377 8.59754 17.1489 8.26545C16.8601 7.93337 16.4401 7.74483 16 7.74983H11.5Z" fill="white" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M6.25 9.16693H4.2475C3.36888 9.15139 2.61779 9.87918 2.5 10.75V16C2.61779 16.8708 3.36888 17.5155 4.2475 17.5H6.25V9.16693Z" fill="var(--label-text-color)" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>강사 만족</div><div class="Card_contentWrapper__opy6W"><div class="Card_content__NS5ju"><img alt="&quot;&quot;" loading="lazy" width="40" height="28" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Card_quote__kt5XP" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 1x, https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 2x" src="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover"/><div class="Card_contentText__rQUT9">공부를 하다가 <b>궁금한 게 생기면 주강사님께 실시간</b>으로 바로 물어볼 수 있다는 점이 너무 좋았습니다.</div></div><div class="Card_caption__BunOL">스프린트 수료생 | 정OO 님</div></div></div></div><div class="Hero_reviewContainer__FMklZ Hero_mobileVisible__uJhVE"><div class="Card_container__pb9Ya"><div class="Label_label__UEEIG Label_blue__hQlvE"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="thumbUp"><path d="M11.5 7.74983V4.74983C11.5 3.50718 10.4927 2.49982 9.25 2.49982L6.25 9.24983V17.4998H14.965C15.713 17.5083 16.3529 16.9644 16.465 16.2248L17.5 9.47483C17.566 9.0397 17.4377 8.59754 17.1489 8.26545C16.8601 7.93337 16.4401 7.74483 16 7.74983H11.5Z" fill="white" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M6.25 9.16693H4.2475C3.36888 9.15139 2.61779 9.87918 2.5 10.75V16C2.61779 16.8708 3.36888 17.5155 4.2475 17.5H6.25V9.16693Z" fill="var(--label-text-color)" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>취업 지원 만족</div><div class="Card_contentWrapper__opy6W"><div class="Card_content__NS5ju"><img alt="&quot;&quot;" loading="lazy" width="40" height="28" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Card_quote__kt5XP" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 1x, https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 2x" src="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover"/><div class="Card_contentText__rQUT9">멘토님께서 <b>1을 물어보면 10을 대답해 주시고</b>, 질문이 없으면 <b>직접 멘토링할 만한 내용을 찾아와 알려주셔서</b> 감동받았습니다.</div></div><div class="Card_caption__BunOL">스프린트 수료생 | 김OO 님</div></div></div></div><div class="Hero_reviewContainer__FMklZ Hero_visible__rbqGu"><div class="Card_container__pb9Ya"><div class="Label_label__UEEIG Label_yellow__EMyGK"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="thumbUp"><path d="M11.5 7.74983V4.74983C11.5 3.50718 10.4927 2.49982 9.25 2.49982L6.25 9.24983V17.4998H14.965C15.713 17.5083 16.3529 16.9644 16.465 16.2248L17.5 9.47483C17.566 9.0397 17.4377 8.59754 17.1489 8.26545C16.8601 7.93337 16.4401 7.74483 16 7.74983H11.5Z" fill="white" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M6.25 9.16693H4.2475C3.36888 9.15139 2.61779 9.87918 2.5 10.75V16C2.61779 16.8708 3.36888 17.5155 4.2475 17.5H6.25V9.16693Z" fill="var(--label-text-color)" stroke="#333236" stroke-width="0.833333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>강사 만족</div><div class="Card_contentWrapper__opy6W"><div class="Card_content__NS5ju"><img alt="&quot;&quot;" loading="lazy" width="40" height="28" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Card_quote__kt5XP" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 1x, https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover 2x" src="https://codeit-static.codeit.com/_sprint-admissions/production/_next/static/media/quote.c119ab08.png?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;t=cover"/><div class="Card_contentText__rQUT9">언제나 도움을 요청할 수 있는 강사님이 있어서, <b>마주한 문제와 판단하기 어려운 것들을 바로 해결 할 수 있어 도움</b>이 되었습니다.</div></div><div class="Card_caption__BunOL">스프린트 수료생 | 박OO 님</div></div></div></div><div class="Hero_reviewContainer__FMklZ Hero_visible__rbqGu Hero_mobileVisible__uJhVE"><div class="Card_container__pb9Ya"><div class="Label_label__UEEIG purple"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="thum